        <heading>1436.1.  Depositions by telephone</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1436.1.  Depositions by telephone
If agreed upon by every party to an action or if ordered by the court, a
deposition may be taken by telephone or other remote electronic means.</p>
        </content>
